{"type": "excalidraw", "version": 2, "source": "excalidraw-diagram-skill", "elements": [{"type": "rectangle", "id": "darkbg", "x": -4000, "y": -3000, "width": 10000, "height": 7500, "backgroundColor": "#1e1e2e", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "transparent", "strokeWidth": 0, "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100}, {"type": "text", "id": "title1", "x": 20, "y": 10, "width": 300, "height": 28, "text": "Automatic Batching 적용 범위", "fontSize": 20, "strokeColor": "#e5e5e5", "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle", "opacity": 100}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "box2", "x": 20, "y": 45, "width": 300, "height": 184, "backgroundColor": "#1e3a5f", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#4a9eed", "strokeWidth": 2, "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "roundness": {"type": 3}}, {"type": "text", "id": "txt3", "x": 35, "y": 60, "width": 270, "height": 154, "text": "상황  React 17  React 18+\n이벤트 핸들러  ✅ 배칭  ✅ 배칭\nsetTimeout  ❌ 개별  ✅ 배칭\nPromise.then  ❌ 개별  ✅ 배칭\nfetch 콜백  ❌ 개별  ✅ 배칭\naddEventListener  ❌ 개별  ✅ 배칭\nqueueMicrotask  ❌ 개별  ✅ 배칭", "fontSize": 14, "strokeColor": "#e5e5e5", "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "middle", "opacity": 100, "containerId": "box2"}], "appState": {"viewBackgroundColor": "#1e1e2e"}}